"{\"uid\": \"allkpop.com-article-2024-09-kiss-of-life-prepares-for-their-first-world-tour-starting-at-olympic-hall\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  4913    KISS OF LIFEis set to perform at Olympic Hall just one year after their debut.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 88, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"KISS OF LIFE will kick off their first world tour,'KISS ROAD', with concerts at Seoul's Olympic Park Olympic Hall on October 26th and 27th.\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"score\": 0.9999999884244063, \"rank\": 9.869478556749609e-09, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This marks a significant achievement for the rising girl group.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having debuted on July 5th of last year, KISS OF LIFE has seen rapid growth over the past year, and now, in their second year, they are preparing for their first solo concert.\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The group is planning a unique setlist that fans rarely get to see.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With solid vocal skills as their foundation, they will deliver special performances, and the stage production will also receive meticulous attention.\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the Seoul concerts, KISS OF LIFE will head to North America, where they will tour 20 cities, including Chicago, Atlanta, Houston, Dallas, Los Angeles, and Las Vegas.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 711, \"end\": 716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"score\": 0.9999999884244063, \"rank\": 9.869478556749609e-09, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour